sap.suite.ui.generic.template.extensionA.constructorDescription:
API to be used for navigation in extensions of Smart Template Applications. Breakout coding can access an instance
of this class via {@link sap.suite.ui.generic.template.ListReport.extensionAPI.ExtensionAPI} or
{@link sap.suite.ui.generic.template.ObjectPage.extensionAPI.ExtensionAPI}. Do not instantiate yourself.

sap.suite.ui.generic.template.ObjectPage.constructorDescription: API to be used in extensions of ObjectPage. Breakout coding can access an instance of this class via this.extensionAPI. Do not instantiate yourself.
Draft transaction controller to be used in extensions of ObjectPage. Breakout coding can access an instance of this class via ExtensionAPI.getTransactionController. Do not instantiate yourself.

sap.suite.ui.generic.template.ListReport.constructorDescription: API to be used in extensions of ListReport. Breakout coding can access an instance of this class via this.extensionAPI. Do not instantiate yourself.

Non draft transaction controller to be used in extensions of ListReport. Breakout coding can access an instance of this class via ExtensionAPI.getTransactionController. Do not instantiate yourself. Note: Only one object can be edited at a given point in time.

sap.suite.ui.generic.template.ObjectPage.constructorDescription: Non Draft transaction controller to be used in extensions of ObjectPage. Breakout coding can access an instance of this class via ExtensionAPI.getTransactionController. Do not instantiate yourself.

sap.suite.ui.generic.template.name: sap.suite.ui.generic.template
sap.suite.ui.generic.template.description: Library with generic Suite UI templates.
sap.suite.ui.generic.template.helpDescription: Library with generic Suite UI templates.

sap.suite.ui.generic.template.Analytical.constructorDescription: API to be used in extensions of AnalyticalListPage. Breakout coding can access an instance of this class via this.extensionAPI. Do not instantiate yourself.

sap.suite.ui.generic.template.Canvas.ext.constructorDescription: API to be used in extensions of Canvas. Breakout coding can access an instance of this class via this.extensionAPI. Do not instantiate yourself.
